text:
Food is decent but there is no standard in pricing. Signboard indicated 1 meat and 2 veg is $2.90. However, I was being charged $3.60.
Upon enquiry, I was told that the meat and green veg is $2.50 while the eggplant is $1.10. What  an expensive eggplant!
Better to patronize Ciyuan Hawker instead.
This plate of food w/o rice costs $4.90 (Veg each costs $1.20 and 2 miserable pieces of chicken costs $1.30). The veg were drowned in oil. Not tasty and not worth coming back
The food taste like shir and the aunty there very bad attitude
